snippet.title: Paralegal Reacts To SUBPOENA SPREE by Heard! Nobody is safe.. LAPD, Twitter, 3rd Grade Teacher..
snippet.description:
PARALEGAL REACTS TO JOHNNY DEPP V. AMBER HEARD

So Amber has subpoenaed everyone and their mom at this point. I think this really displays her desperation, she is on a "fishing expedition" to try to hopefully find something. It's clear from the very generalized disclosure requests she doesn't have anything, she is hoping to find something or to try to push a narrative. Johnny on the other hand is very selective and deliberate with his subpoenas, which means there is a purpose to it and his counsel know exactly where they want to go with the line of questioning. 

What do you think about all the people Amber subpoenaed? Let me know your comments down below, I love chatting about this with you guys! 

Also gonna link Lost Beyond Pluto, who is a lawyer who breaks down the legality of this case very professionally: https://www.youtube.com/c/lostbeyondpluto

Link to Incredibly Average, he has covered this case in depth from beginning to very recently.. including animated re-enactments etc. Highly recommend!: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCg0C-N_MPYYOXyF4T3jMxNQ

Thank you so much for the love on my last videos I really appreciate it! It's really motivating me to keep it up. I hope this was helpful or enjoyable in some way. I plan to keep up with this case so stay tuned and make sure you are subscribed and turn your notification bell on!
